WEBVTT

01:38.120 --> 01:40.580
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.360 --> 01:43.680
[Episode 2]

01:52.430 --> 01:53.070
Lu Huai.

01:53.560 --> 01:55.870
You'll be executed the day after tomorrow.

01:55.870 --> 01:56.430
Although your case

01:56.430 --> 01:58.039
was tried by
the Court of Judicial Review itself

01:58.039 --> 02:00.000
and the verdict is already set in stone,

02:00.000 --> 02:01.400
according to procedure,

02:01.510 --> 02:02.680
I still have to ask:

02:03.640 --> 02:04.310
Lord Lu,

02:04.840 --> 02:06.560
do you have any grievances to declare

02:06.560 --> 02:07.760
or any case to appeal?

02:09.710 --> 02:10.240
No.

02:12.360 --> 02:13.190
I was thinking

02:13.360 --> 02:15.080
I might as well marry a death row prisoner

02:15.080 --> 02:17.150
to dispel the negative energy around me.

02:17.150 --> 02:18.430
I'd also offer some money

02:18.430 --> 02:19.890
to compensate his family.

02:20.960 --> 02:22.090
But unfortunately,

02:22.240 --> 02:23.170
he has no family,

02:23.960 --> 02:25.690
not even relatives or friends.

02:26.840 --> 02:28.400
Actually, this Lord Lu

02:28.430 --> 02:29.760
used to be quite decent.

02:30.310 --> 02:31.680
Though somewhat lazy,

02:31.840 --> 02:33.300
he was fair as an official.

02:33.590 --> 02:35.590
He's been working here in Wei County
for 5 or 6 years

02:35.590 --> 02:37.590
and never oppressed any civilians.

02:38.300 --> 02:39.210
I don't know why

02:39.240 --> 02:40.570
he suddenly lost his way

02:40.630 --> 02:42.690
and committed such a terrible crime.

02:43.310 --> 02:44.710
I visited his residence.

02:44.910 --> 02:46.840
It was very empty

02:47.120 --> 02:48.120
and quite simple.

02:48.430 --> 02:49.800
I just don't understand,

02:49.800 --> 02:50.710
with no family,

02:51.190 --> 02:52.430
what's the point of
embezzling so much money?

02:52.430 --> 02:53.630
What use could it be to him?

02:53.630 --> 02:54.590
Who knows?

02:56.120 --> 02:57.800
That's why I have a feeling that

02:57.800 --> 02:59.680
he doesn't seem like that kind of person.

02:59.680 --> 03:00.810
Don't overthink it.

03:01.430 --> 03:03.320
You've already joined the immortal sect.

03:03.320 --> 03:04.560
You shouldn't be involved in these

03:04.560 --> 03:05.710
worldly matters.

03:06.360 --> 03:08.890
You only had a few days of connection
with him.

03:09.030 --> 03:10.830
There's no need to know too much,

03:10.870 --> 03:13.130
lest it brings you
unnecessary trouble.

03:24.390 --> 03:27.010
[Wei County Government]

03:27.680 --> 03:28.630
This case

03:28.800 --> 03:30.750
didn't need such a severe sentence.

03:30.750 --> 03:31.750
It was only because

03:31.750 --> 03:33.940
he insisted on getting Lord Liang involved

03:33.940 --> 03:35.400
that it ended up like this.

03:36.079 --> 03:38.520
If he'd be willing to submit
a formal petition

03:38.520 --> 03:39.850
and admit his mistakes,

03:40.340 --> 03:42.140
then even if he'd be sentenced to

03:42.190 --> 03:42.850
beheading,

03:43.400 --> 03:46.329
it would still be far better than
death by 1,000 cuts.

03:48.360 --> 03:48.870
My Lord.

03:50.430 --> 03:52.190
You are kind-hearted, My Lord.

03:52.710 --> 03:54.430
It's Lu Huai who's being unreasonable.

03:54.430 --> 03:56.310
Even if he's lucky enough to escape
this time,

03:56.310 --> 03:57.710
he won't escape the next.

03:58.079 --> 03:59.130
Lu Huai

03:59.310 --> 04:00.120
is an orphan.

04:00.870 --> 04:01.910
His parents died early,

04:01.910 --> 04:03.570
and he has no other relatives.

04:03.910 --> 04:05.640
He came from the frontier army.

04:05.870 --> 04:06.620
After earning several military merits

04:06.620 --> 04:07.770
at the frontier,

04:07.910 --> 04:08.750
he was recommended by someone

04:08.750 --> 04:10.610
and then appointed to Wei County.

04:11.910 --> 04:12.680
Why is it stated here that

04:12.680 --> 04:13.810
he still has family?

04:14.960 --> 04:16.750
This was newly recorded
a couple of days ago.

04:16.750 --> 04:18.190
He recently got married,

04:18.360 --> 04:20.120
to a woman who's also from Wei County.

04:20.120 --> 04:21.180
Her surname's Xin.

04:25.160 --> 04:28.280
[Madam Lu, née Xin. The rest's unknown.]

04:28.680 --> 04:29.750
Here's your dish, Sir.

04:29.750 --> 04:30.550
Please enjoy.

04:30.630 --> 04:31.490
Have you heard?

04:31.600 --> 04:33.330
Lu Huai is going to be executed.

04:33.950 --> 04:34.830
If you ask me, Lu Huai

04:34.830 --> 04:36.230
brought it upon himself.

04:36.270 --> 04:37.480
He leveraged those few military merits

04:37.480 --> 04:38.560
to snag an official position,

04:38.560 --> 04:39.870
yet he showed no gratitude.

04:39.870 --> 04:41.680
Instead, he colluded with
corrupt merchants

04:41.680 --> 04:42.720
and drove up grain prices,

04:42.720 --> 04:44.480
causing the deaths of countless people!

04:44.480 --> 04:45.940
Money corrupts the heart.

04:46.000 --> 04:47.400
For him to do such things,

04:47.600 --> 04:48.159
who knows

04:48.360 --> 04:49.960
how much he profited from it?

04:50.120 --> 04:51.920
Thankfully, Lord Liang
was wise

04:52.040 --> 04:54.070
and sentenced him
to death by 1,000 cuts.

04:54.070 --> 04:54.680
It's truly

04:54.870 --> 04:55.850
satisfying to see justice served.

04:55.850 --> 04:56.800
It's truly satisfying!

04:56.800 --> 04:57.530
Yes, indeed.

04:58.000 --> 04:59.600
Attendant, the bill please!

05:00.830 --> 05:02.750
You gentlemen are supposedly
well-educated scholars,

05:02.750 --> 05:04.160
yet you don't investigate
the truth behind matters.

05:03.820 --> 05:06.740
[Tang You]

05:04.360 --> 05:05.870
You only repeat what others say,

05:05.870 --> 05:07.040
barking at shadows like dogs,

05:07.040 --> 05:08.310
and you still have the nerve to sit here

05:08.310 --> 05:10.070
talking so shamelessly.

05:10.360 --> 05:11.480
It's truly laughable.

05:11.480 --> 05:12.560
Who are you talking about?

05:12.560 --> 05:13.690
You guys, of course.

05:13.830 --> 05:15.240
A bunch of fools
ignorant of the law,

05:15.240 --> 05:16.160
unable to tell right from wrong,

05:16.160 --> 05:17.800
and incapable of discerning
the wise from the foolish.

05:17.800 --> 05:18.720
Who are you?

05:18.920 --> 05:20.750
We're just
having a casual conversation here.

05:20.750 --> 05:22.430
What does it have to do with you?

05:22.430 --> 05:23.720
What you're saying is wrong,

05:23.720 --> 05:24.950
and I can't stand hearing it.

05:24.950 --> 05:25.810
Can't stand it?

05:26.160 --> 05:27.000
Could it be

05:27.270 --> 05:29.190
you're a supporter of
that corrupt official,

05:29.190 --> 05:30.270
and since your boss is about to die,

05:30.270 --> 05:31.390
you said that out of fear?

05:31.390 --> 05:32.450
Corrupt official?

05:32.750 --> 05:33.950
Just look at you guys—

05:34.040 --> 05:34.830
ignorant, petty, jealous

05:34.830 --> 05:36.360
good-for-nothings—

05:36.390 --> 05:37.560
the fact that even people like you
managed to

05:37.560 --> 05:38.480
survive that flood

05:38.480 --> 05:39.120
shows that

05:39.830 --> 05:41.560
he still wasn't greedy enough.

05:44.120 --> 05:44.520
You...

05:46.120 --> 05:46.600
Ignore him.

05:46.600 --> 05:47.090
Miss!

05:47.140 --> 05:47.560
Let's have a drink together.

05:47.560 --> 05:47.830
Please settle the bill.

05:47.830 --> 05:48.890
Alright, alright.

05:49.870 --> 05:50.930
Please come again.

05:52.360 --> 05:54.690
Come take a look!
Check out what we've got!

06:09.730 --> 06:10.790
Who are you people?

06:11.000 --> 06:12.330
Who are you looking for?

06:13.000 --> 06:14.120
Are you Mrs. Lu,

06:16.310 --> 06:17.640
Lord Lu Huai's wife?

06:18.800 --> 06:19.330
Yes, I am.

06:20.220 --> 06:21.040
Officers, may I ask

06:21.040 --> 06:22.240
what brings you here?

06:22.600 --> 06:23.310
The day after tomorrow

06:23.310 --> 06:24.510
is his execution day.

06:24.630 --> 06:25.510
According to the rules,

06:25.510 --> 06:26.510
family members can visit the prison
one last time

06:26.510 --> 06:27.510
to say their final goodbyes.

06:27.510 --> 06:29.160
It must be no later than 7 PM tomorrow.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.290
Don't miss the time.

06:31.270 --> 06:32.330
Final goodbyes...

06:36.270 --> 06:37.800
Didn't you say you were leaving?

06:37.800 --> 06:38.800
Yes, I am leaving.

06:39.100 --> 06:41.190
I haven't finished the tasks
my master assigned me,

06:41.190 --> 06:42.790
and I can't delay any longer.

06:43.630 --> 06:44.890
I've found the flower.

06:45.159 --> 06:46.090
When I was there,

06:46.159 --> 06:47.620
I ran into 2 young beggars.

06:47.800 --> 06:49.240
They probably saw the house was empty

06:49.240 --> 06:50.000
and moved in.

06:50.360 --> 06:52.090
Want me to go and chase them out?

06:52.870 --> 06:53.670
Don't bother.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.570
The house's rented anyway.

06:55.750 --> 06:56.830
When the time comes,

06:56.830 --> 06:58.560
the landlord will take it back.

06:59.920 --> 07:01.450
What kind of flower is this?

07:03.510 --> 07:04.480
Hidden-heart Orchid.

07:04.480 --> 07:05.740
Hidden-heart Orchid?

07:06.480 --> 07:07.480
Never heard of it.

07:08.430 --> 07:09.030
By the way,

07:09.830 --> 07:11.510
I heard you're from the western border,

07:11.510 --> 07:12.310
so I asked around about

07:12.310 --> 07:13.680
some customs from your region.

07:13.680 --> 07:15.870
They say that a person
must be buried in new clothes

07:15.870 --> 07:17.360
to have a smooth journey to the afterlife,

07:17.360 --> 07:18.750
avoid being reborn as animals,

07:18.750 --> 07:21.410
and be able to live with dignity
in the next life.

07:21.920 --> 07:22.480
I didn't know

07:22.480 --> 07:23.830
what colors and styles you like,

07:23.830 --> 07:24.870
so I made a set

07:24.950 --> 07:26.410
according to my own taste.

07:30.240 --> 07:30.970
Thanks a lot.

07:32.360 --> 07:33.620
Do you want to try it on?

07:34.430 --> 07:35.120
No need.

07:35.870 --> 07:37.870
In the end, I'll just be nothing but
a pile of bones anyway.

07:37.870 --> 07:40.800
As long as something wraps around me,
that's enough.

07:42.159 --> 07:42.820
Time to eat.

07:47.480 --> 07:48.630
This is the farewell meal.

07:48.630 --> 07:50.430
Eat well for your final journey.

07:56.920 --> 07:57.720
Just routine.

08:00.800 --> 08:02.060
Why aren't you eating?

08:03.600 --> 08:05.000
I don't feel like eating.

08:09.070 --> 08:09.560
Lord Lu,

08:10.270 --> 08:11.480
is there truly no injustice

08:11.480 --> 08:12.510
in your case?

08:14.480 --> 08:16.010
Public opinion has spoken.

08:16.310 --> 08:18.170
How could there be any injustice?

08:18.600 --> 08:20.000
I just can't help feeling

08:20.270 --> 08:21.600
you're not a bad person.

08:23.310 --> 08:25.120
The Court of Judicial Review
itself determined my crimes

08:25.120 --> 08:27.040
and sentenced me
to death by 1,000 cuts.

08:27.040 --> 08:28.840
Over 100 memorials from censors

08:29.040 --> 08:29.870
have been submitted

08:29.870 --> 08:31.270
to impeach me,

08:31.390 --> 08:32.549
and the common people out there

08:32.549 --> 08:33.200
all curse me

08:33.200 --> 08:35.000
as a greedy and treacherous man.

08:35.669 --> 08:36.799
You've heard it all,

08:37.030 --> 08:38.360
so why do you still think

08:38.720 --> 08:39.850
I'm not a bad person?

08:40.510 --> 08:41.720
Public clamor can confound
right and wrong.

08:41.720 --> 08:43.520
Give a dog a bad name and hang him.

08:43.549 --> 08:45.200
Though we haven't interacted much,

08:45.200 --> 08:46.910
I feel that you're not the same as

08:46.910 --> 08:48.840
what's being said about you out there.

08:48.840 --> 08:49.670
If you were truly

08:49.670 --> 08:50.870
greedy and cowardly,

08:51.080 --> 08:53.270
you'd have come asking me for help, right?

08:53.270 --> 08:54.790
After all, in the eyes of the world,

08:54.790 --> 08:56.050
I'm also a cultivator.

08:56.750 --> 08:57.480
Don't you...

08:58.480 --> 08:59.360
Want to live?

09:01.120 --> 09:03.440
You can know someone's face
but not their heart.

09:03.440 --> 09:05.360
You've only known me for a few days,

09:05.360 --> 09:07.690
so how much can you possibly
know about me?

09:10.870 --> 09:12.530
Don't trust others so easily.

09:13.270 --> 09:14.720
The human heart is treacherous—

09:14.720 --> 09:16.270
far more complex and unpredictable

09:16.270 --> 09:17.960
than the matters of cultivation.

09:17.960 --> 09:19.020
It's always better

09:19.320 --> 09:20.180
to be cautious.

09:27.440 --> 09:28.500
It's getting late.

09:29.320 --> 09:30.320
You should go now.

09:47.900 --> 09:50.540
[Xin Xie Manor]

10:21.730 --> 10:25.900
[Sheng, Xin Xie Manor]

10:26.240 --> 10:27.390
I still have some matters

10:27.390 --> 10:28.150
to take care of here,

10:28.150 --> 10:29.910
so it'll be a while before I can return.

10:29.910 --> 10:30.390
Also,

10:30.440 --> 10:32.000
Sheng is very obedient and well-behaved.

10:32.000 --> 10:33.030
If you don't provoke her,

10:33.030 --> 10:34.480
she won't give you any trouble.

10:34.480 --> 10:36.120
You two get along well at home

10:36.360 --> 10:37.890
and wait for me to come back.

10:38.840 --> 10:39.960
I still have some matters

10:39.960 --> 10:40.790
to take care of here,

10:40.790 --> 10:42.550
so it'll be a while before I can return.

10:42.550 --> 10:43.000
Also,

10:43.120 --> 10:44.670
Sheng is very obedient and well-behaved.

10:44.670 --> 10:45.630
If you don't provoke her,

10:45.630 --> 10:47.360
she won't give you any trouble.

10:49.600 --> 10:54.390
♪ The moon rises, bright and fair ♪

10:54.670 --> 10:59.270
♪ A graceful beauty, soft and rare ♪

10:59.790 --> 11:03.630
♪ She soothes my troubled,
restless heart ♪

11:04.600 --> 11:08.390
♪ So elegant and radiant ♪

11:05.180 --> 11:08.520
[Madam Flower]

11:09.030 --> 11:11.150
♪ Soft and swaying ♪

11:23.910 --> 11:25.550
The Chongling Valley
Pill-Tasting Competition

11:25.550 --> 11:26.880
is still some time away.

11:27.510 --> 11:28.150
So be it.

11:28.630 --> 11:31.430
I'll take shelter from the rain
at the inn tonight.

11:37.080 --> 11:37.750
Wake up.

11:38.600 --> 11:39.270
Wake up now.

11:45.550 --> 11:46.280
Excuse me...

11:46.550 --> 11:48.050
[An]

11:47.390 --> 11:48.150
Leave.

11:51.200 --> 11:52.270
Hurry up and leave.

11:59.750 --> 12:01.440
It's about to rain outside.

12:01.840 --> 12:03.300
Where are you going, Miss?

12:04.930 --> 12:06.460
Could it be my humble inn is too shabby

12:06.460 --> 12:08.120
to meet your standards, Miss?

12:08.790 --> 12:10.510
I forgot to feed my horse.

12:11.000 --> 12:12.460
I can send someone to do it.

12:12.550 --> 12:14.810
How could I trouble you to do it yourself?

12:15.000 --> 12:15.480
An,

12:15.910 --> 12:16.440
go do it.

12:21.440 --> 12:22.570
Please, have a seat.

12:27.910 --> 12:29.170
Your hands are so cold.

12:29.510 --> 12:30.810
Let me get you some warm wine

12:30.810 --> 12:31.760
to warm you up.

12:48.120 --> 12:50.480
Wine... Wine...

12:50.720 --> 12:51.670
Wine!

12:52.240 --> 12:53.000
Landlady,

12:53.360 --> 12:54.480
2 more jars please.

12:55.440 --> 12:56.390
Great wine.

12:57.270 --> 12:58.270
It's him.

12:58.580 --> 13:05.200
[Fulai Inn]

13:22.440 --> 13:23.360
Come with me quickly.

13:23.360 --> 13:25.030
Why? Where to?

13:25.510 --> 13:27.240
Stop drinking and come with me.

13:27.440 --> 13:29.170
I haven't finished my wine yet.

13:29.510 --> 13:30.460
Come with me, you.

13:30.460 --> 13:31.790
Sorry for the wait, Sir.

13:32.360 --> 13:33.960
Fine wine's coming right up.

13:40.440 --> 13:42.170
Sorry to keep you waiting, Sir.

13:44.790 --> 13:45.590
Please enjoy.

13:50.960 --> 13:52.090
Here comes the wine.

13:55.390 --> 13:56.870
Thank you for your kindness, Landlady,

13:56.870 --> 13:57.870
but I don't drink.

13:58.390 --> 13:59.480
This wine only warms the body.

13:59.480 --> 14:00.810
It won't make you drunk.

14:01.510 --> 14:03.370
This wine doesn't make you drunk.

14:03.550 --> 14:05.480
That's how you know it's good wine.

14:12.140 --> 14:13.800
Listen to him. Just take a sip.

14:14.600 --> 14:15.910
I think I'll still pass.

14:15.910 --> 14:16.840
Come on.

14:26.350 --> 14:27.860
Who dares disturb my sleep?

14:27.600 --> 14:30.140
[Lord of Rust-Sword, bounty guard
of Dongzhou Prefecture]

14:34.240 --> 14:35.570
Sir, if you wish to stay,

14:35.750 --> 14:37.480
there are comfortable beds upstairs.

14:37.480 --> 14:38.630
If you want to continue your journey,

14:38.630 --> 14:40.910
we have raincoats and umbrellas to offer.

14:40.910 --> 14:42.630
How come you went and slept on my beam

14:42.630 --> 14:44.150
without saying a word?

14:44.670 --> 14:47.330
That's hardly the conduct of
a gentleman, is it?

14:48.240 --> 14:49.200
I'm an official,

14:49.600 --> 14:50.520
not a gentleman.

14:50.520 --> 14:51.390
I don't like sleeping in beds,

14:51.390 --> 14:53.320
nor do I enjoy going out in the rain.

14:53.390 --> 14:54.990
I just want a sip of warm wine.

15:02.600 --> 15:03.270
Landlady,

15:03.560 --> 15:05.360
why don't you join me for a drink?

15:09.080 --> 15:09.880
What's wrong?

15:10.150 --> 15:11.950
Won't you give me this courtesy?

15:12.080 --> 15:14.280
I have no intention of being your enemy.

15:15.120 --> 15:16.050
Unfortunately,

15:16.600 --> 15:18.720
someone has reported you
to the Dongzhou Prefecture,

15:18.720 --> 15:20.240
saying you got hungry at midnight

15:20.240 --> 15:21.670
and devoured someone's husband.

15:21.670 --> 15:23.030
I've come to claim the bounty.

15:23.030 --> 15:24.550
I'm afraid this calamity today

15:24.550 --> 15:25.950
is one you cannot escape.

15:26.360 --> 15:27.560
You have a death wish?

15:47.330 --> 15:47.840
You,

15:48.250 --> 15:49.650
take that drunkard away!

15:55.600 --> 15:56.200
Wake up!

15:57.240 --> 15:57.970
Come with me!

16:20.150 --> 16:21.150
Sit down for a bit.

16:57.440 --> 16:59.000
I thought it was a snake or scorpion,

16:59.000 --> 17:01.130
but it's just a red-headed centipede.

17:04.510 --> 17:05.569
What are you doing?

17:06.200 --> 17:07.510
Celestial stem Ding, earthly branch Si,

17:07.510 --> 17:10.109
the five elements rotation
requires yin fire.

17:13.270 --> 17:14.069
Interesting.

17:14.390 --> 17:16.720
I didn't expect that you're a cultivator.

17:51.070 --> 17:52.670
It was actually an illusion?

17:59.160 --> 17:59.830
It's dead?

18:01.790 --> 18:02.850
Well, I stepped in.

18:02.940 --> 18:05.000
Of course I could take down a mere bug.

18:07.580 --> 18:09.070
Since I can't bring back its head,

18:09.070 --> 18:10.150
a hairpin will do.

18:10.640 --> 18:12.550
You said you came to claim the bounty,

18:12.550 --> 18:14.030
and you're in an official uniform.

18:14.030 --> 18:15.760
Are you a government official?

18:18.590 --> 18:20.320
I stand by my name and reputation.

18:20.320 --> 18:21.480
I'm a bounty guard from
Dongzhou Prefecture,

18:21.480 --> 18:23.080
known as Lord of Rust-Sword.

18:23.680 --> 18:25.340
I'm Xin Mei from Xin Xie Manor.

18:26.790 --> 18:28.640
You're a mediocre cultivator
with average talent

18:28.640 --> 18:30.200
and ordinary martial skills,

18:30.200 --> 18:31.850
yet you've got quite some nerve,

18:31.850 --> 18:32.880
daring to enter
a shabby little inn like this

18:32.880 --> 18:33.790
in the middle of nowhere.

18:33.790 --> 18:35.110
I just came in
to take shelter from the rain.

18:35.110 --> 18:36.710
I didn't think much about it.

18:37.550 --> 18:38.750
So it was not bravery,

18:38.910 --> 18:40.310
but rather foolishness.

18:40.310 --> 18:40.710
You...

18:45.030 --> 18:47.360
Anyway, thank you for your help, Warrior.

18:48.550 --> 18:50.210
If you really want to thank me,

18:50.510 --> 18:51.570
give me some money.

18:51.760 --> 18:52.830
I've been chasing this centipede demon

18:52.830 --> 18:53.920
for over 300 li,

18:54.440 --> 18:55.840
and my boots are worn out.

18:59.960 --> 19:01.160
You don't have money?

19:01.480 --> 19:03.880
My master did give me some
when I left the mountain,

19:03.880 --> 19:04.640
but now

19:04.720 --> 19:06.250
I've spent almost all of it.

19:08.830 --> 19:10.830
Landlady, I've fed the horse and...

19:28.880 --> 19:30.810
Now we know what to have for dinner.

19:32.590 --> 19:34.320
Go get some firewood to start a fire.

19:34.320 --> 19:35.350
This room is cold and damp.

19:35.350 --> 19:36.150
I'm freezing.

19:54.000 --> 19:56.070
This little rabbit demon
hasn't harmed anyone.

19:56.070 --> 19:56.930
How do you know?

19:57.550 --> 19:59.280
It's been trembling with fear.

19:59.720 --> 20:00.160
Go on.

20:05.960 --> 20:07.640
Why did you let it go?

20:08.550 --> 20:09.680
Whether human or demon,

20:09.680 --> 20:10.920
there's always good and evil,
right and wrong.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.440
This little rabbit
hasn't done anything wrong,

20:12.440 --> 20:13.840
so you shouldn't hurt it.

20:14.480 --> 20:14.960
Fine.

20:15.400 --> 20:17.000
All that effort for nothing.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.200
Miss cultivator,

20:21.750 --> 20:22.810
can you mend boots?

20:23.550 --> 20:24.030
No.

20:25.650 --> 20:26.550
You have no skills whatsoever,

20:26.550 --> 20:28.010
yet you dare travel alone?

20:28.790 --> 20:30.190
Are you a cultivator too?

20:30.550 --> 20:32.210
You've never heard of my name?

20:34.830 --> 20:36.790
I'm ranked second
on the List of Top Martial Artists,

20:36.790 --> 20:38.520
known as "Lord of Rust-Sword."

20:39.030 --> 20:39.820
I'm a human,

20:40.030 --> 20:41.030
not a cultivator.

20:41.590 --> 20:42.720
That's impressive,

20:42.720 --> 20:43.750
being able to fight evil spirits

20:43.750 --> 20:44.750
as a mere mortal.

20:46.110 --> 20:46.830
Of course.

20:47.350 --> 20:49.000
I aim to achieve sainthood
through martial arts.

20:49.000 --> 20:50.830
Once my divine sword is unsheathed,

20:50.830 --> 20:52.110
no demons or monsters,

20:52.400 --> 20:53.590
not even
immortal sect cultivators,

20:53.590 --> 20:54.920
will be a match for me.

21:01.640 --> 21:02.440
You're awake.

21:05.790 --> 21:06.720
Have some water.

21:15.310 --> 21:16.240
Thank you, Miss.

21:17.790 --> 21:19.000
I was drunk earlier.

21:19.480 --> 21:21.000
I drank myself into a stupor,

21:21.000 --> 21:22.860
and now my stomach feels bloated.

21:22.920 --> 21:24.050
It feels really bad.

21:27.200 --> 21:27.930
Mr. scholar.

21:28.830 --> 21:29.720
Do you have any money?

21:29.720 --> 21:30.160
Money?

21:38.200 --> 21:38.730
Yes, I do.

21:39.070 --> 21:40.640
I'm heading to the capital
for the imperial exam,

21:40.640 --> 21:42.440
and I brought some travel funds.

21:45.030 --> 21:45.550
Look,

21:46.350 --> 21:48.010
the road to the capital is dangerous.

21:48.010 --> 21:48.920
You should get yourself a guard

21:48.920 --> 21:50.520
to escort you to the capital.

21:52.350 --> 21:53.680
That won't be necessary.

21:53.680 --> 21:54.740
The money I brought

21:54.960 --> 21:56.420
is only enough for myself.

22:14.240 --> 22:15.300
I'm going to sleep.

22:15.310 --> 22:16.240
Do as you please.

22:23.350 --> 22:25.010
Thank you for the water, Miss.

22:25.070 --> 22:26.270
You're welcome, Sir.

22:27.100 --> 22:27.860
Actually,

22:28.000 --> 22:30.000
this isn't the first time we've met.

22:30.640 --> 22:31.790
That day at Heyan Restaurant,

22:31.790 --> 22:33.190
we had a brief encounter.

22:33.640 --> 22:34.770
What a coincidence.

22:36.350 --> 22:37.680
To be honest with you, Sir,

22:37.680 --> 22:39.010
I have something to ask.

22:40.000 --> 22:40.640
That day I heard

22:40.640 --> 22:41.880
from what you said

22:42.480 --> 22:43.940
that it seems there's more

22:44.200 --> 22:45.200
to Lord Lu's case.

22:45.350 --> 22:46.080
Is that true?

22:47.750 --> 22:50.200
You know Lord Lu, Miss?

22:52.350 --> 22:53.680
Are you from Wei County?

22:54.070 --> 22:54.590
Yes,

22:55.350 --> 22:57.160
but I haven't been home for a long time.

22:57.160 --> 22:58.510
I just returned recently.

22:58.510 --> 22:59.550
Then what do you think

22:59.550 --> 23:01.010
has changed in Wei County?

23:02.070 --> 23:02.960
I think

23:03.510 --> 23:05.720
there aren't many significant changes.

23:05.720 --> 23:06.480
That's odd.

23:07.030 --> 23:08.480
The great flood six months ago,

23:08.480 --> 23:10.000
with 2 months of non-stop rain,

23:10.000 --> 23:10.930
affected all 9 counties of Yong region.

23:10.930 --> 23:11.790
Walls collapsed,

23:11.790 --> 23:13.440
families wept, and countless people died.

23:13.440 --> 23:14.270
In Caomen County,

23:14.270 --> 23:15.030
Jiangping County

23:15.030 --> 23:16.090
and Lishan County,

23:16.110 --> 23:17.270
flat lands became rivers,

23:17.270 --> 23:19.200
low areas flooded over 10 feet deep,

23:19.200 --> 23:21.310
and countless homes of officials
and commoners collapsed.

23:21.310 --> 23:22.270
Even today,

23:22.440 --> 23:23.640
there are still few signs of life,

23:23.640 --> 23:24.480
just yellow sand and withered grass,

23:24.480 --> 23:25.480
a vast wasteland.

23:25.750 --> 23:27.840
How could Wei County remain so prosperous?

23:27.840 --> 23:28.760
Perhaps

23:28.790 --> 23:30.250
the flooding in Wei County

23:30.310 --> 23:32.440
wasn't as severe as in other counties?

23:32.830 --> 23:34.070
Wei County is located in a low-lying area

23:34.070 --> 23:35.170
and borders the Cao River.

23:35.170 --> 23:36.800
Its position is even worse

23:36.830 --> 23:37.830
than the other counties.

23:37.830 --> 23:39.490
So why did it remain unharmed?

23:40.000 --> 23:40.550
Why?

23:41.070 --> 23:42.470
It was because of Lord Lu.

23:43.920 --> 23:45.380
Since Lord Lu took office,

23:45.400 --> 23:47.000
he's always focused on repairing the dikes

23:47.000 --> 23:48.070
and reinforcing the levees.

23:48.070 --> 23:49.350
When the flood arrived,

23:49.350 --> 23:50.480
he even led the able-bodied personally,

23:50.480 --> 23:52.720
working day and night,
and it was only through this effort

23:52.720 --> 23:55.250
that Wei County's livelihood
was preserved.

23:56.990 --> 23:58.050
Then does that mean

23:58.550 --> 23:59.680
his defiance of the imperial edict—

23:59.680 --> 24:01.030
his refusal to control grain prices—

24:01.030 --> 24:02.090
was all just an act?

24:02.590 --> 24:03.650
That part was true.

24:07.240 --> 24:08.780
Initially, the 9 counties
jointly ordered

24:08.780 --> 24:10.750
that merchants be forbidden from
inflating grain prices.

24:10.750 --> 24:12.440
Any grain priced above 100 wen per dou

24:12.440 --> 24:13.570
could not be traded.

24:13.750 --> 24:14.480
But Lord Lu

24:14.640 --> 24:16.000
did the exact opposite.

24:16.310 --> 24:17.240
He raised the price of grain

24:17.240 --> 24:18.440
to 180 wen per dou.

24:19.400 --> 24:21.160
The people couldn't afford to eat,

24:21.160 --> 24:22.960
so naturally they resented him.

24:23.370 --> 24:24.500
So why did he do that?

24:25.000 --> 24:26.480
Is it true as people say

24:27.400 --> 24:28.090
that he took...

24:28.090 --> 24:30.420
That he took bribes from grain merchants?

24:32.330 --> 24:34.330
At first, that's what I thought too.

24:34.750 --> 24:36.510
But take a look at
the other 8 counties

24:36.510 --> 24:37.720
that restricted grain prices.

24:37.720 --> 24:39.270
Merchants couldn't sell at high prices,

24:39.270 --> 24:41.320
so they simply hoarded their grain

24:41.350 --> 24:42.440
and refused to sell any,

24:42.440 --> 24:44.570
let alone transport it to Yong region.

24:45.170 --> 24:47.590
The people could only
starve to death at home.

24:47.590 --> 24:48.640
Among the 9 counties,

24:48.640 --> 24:50.590
only Wei County allowed
high-priced grain sales.

24:50.590 --> 24:51.250
As a result,

24:51.400 --> 24:53.600
grain merchants flocked to Wei County.

24:53.820 --> 24:55.350
Scarcity increases value.

24:55.350 --> 24:56.480
With more grain available,

24:56.480 --> 24:58.120
the price actually came down.

24:58.120 --> 24:59.070
Only those who took the trouble

24:59.070 --> 25:00.720
to investigate closely would notice

25:00.720 --> 25:01.960
that Wei County's high-priced grain

25:01.960 --> 25:03.960
was only sold for less than 2 months.

25:04.160 --> 25:05.090
So you're saying

25:05.240 --> 25:06.750
he actually did a good thing?

25:06.750 --> 25:08.210
It was a good thing indeed.

25:08.480 --> 25:09.880
But people only remember

25:10.110 --> 25:11.590
that he drove up grain prices at first,

25:11.590 --> 25:12.920
causing them to starve,

25:13.480 --> 25:15.940
without understanding the bigger picture.

25:16.920 --> 25:18.380
As for the imperial court,

25:19.110 --> 25:21.310
with so many people
starving to death in this disaster,

25:21.310 --> 25:22.970
they needed someone to blame.

25:23.750 --> 25:24.350
But...

25:25.550 --> 25:27.680
I still feel that Lord Lu's punishment

25:27.830 --> 25:29.430
was determined too hastily.

25:29.800 --> 25:30.960
In the past, the Court of Judicial Review

25:30.960 --> 25:32.550
had sentenced officials to
death by 1,000 cuts before,

25:32.550 --> 25:34.160
but such an inhumane and cruel punishment

25:34.160 --> 25:36.040
normally had to be reported step by step—

25:36.040 --> 25:37.640
from the prefecture and county
up to the capital,

25:37.640 --> 25:39.350
until the Emperor approved it.

25:39.350 --> 25:39.750
Yet...

25:39.960 --> 25:41.110
Yet Lord Lu's crime was determined

25:41.110 --> 25:42.510
in less than half a month.

25:43.310 --> 25:44.710
That really was too fast.

25:47.160 --> 25:48.890
If everything you said is true,

25:48.920 --> 25:49.510
then why didn't Lord Lu

25:49.510 --> 25:51.440
appeal or proclaim his innocence?

25:52.350 --> 25:54.150
The 9 counties are in collusion,

25:54.390 --> 25:56.680
all speaking and acting
from the same playbook.

25:56.680 --> 25:57.880
No flaws can be found.

25:58.310 --> 25:59.370
At a time like this,

25:59.400 --> 26:00.680
anyone who acts differently

26:00.680 --> 26:02.480
becomes the one that sticks out—

26:02.480 --> 26:03.400
the scapegoat.

26:07.590 --> 26:08.920
Who could he turn to

26:10.270 --> 26:11.110
for justice?

26:13.310 --> 26:14.770
If that's really the case,

26:15.880 --> 26:16.940
how much injustice

26:17.240 --> 26:18.770
must Lord Lu have suffered?

26:32.960 --> 26:33.440
Lord Lu,

26:34.480 --> 26:36.010
is there truly no injustice

26:36.030 --> 26:37.070
in your case?

26:39.680 --> 26:41.210
Public opinion has spoken.

26:41.480 --> 26:43.340
How could there be any injustice?

26:44.510 --> 26:46.170
Don't trust others so easily.

26:46.790 --> 26:48.400
The human heart is treacherous—

26:48.400 --> 26:49.960
far more complex and unpredictable

26:49.960 --> 26:51.820
than the matters of cultivation.

26:52.310 --> 26:53.370
It's always better

26:53.720 --> 26:54.580
to be cautious.

27:34.200 --> 27:34.790
Lu Huai,

27:35.310 --> 27:36.170
it's time to go.

27:58.380 --> 28:02.380
♪ Caught in fate's design,
I search my soul ♪

28:02.760 --> 28:05.740
♪ What should I do to avoid
living my life in vain? ♪

28:05.770 --> 28:07.490
♪ My blade stays clean,
untouched by dust ♪

28:07.510 --> 28:11.490
♪ Yet it's sparked thousands of wars ♪

28:13.620 --> 28:16.800
♪ Soul consumed, bones remade—
I accept it all ♪

28:16.900 --> 28:20.630
♪ Embracing pain as home,
reborn like a phoenix ♪

28:20.970 --> 28:27.060
♪ Just to trade the rest of my days
for one true life as a human ♪

28:23.310 --> 28:25.840
It's truly satisfying
to see justice served!

28:27.990 --> 28:31.660
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

28:31.680 --> 28:34.740
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

28:34.770 --> 28:37.600
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

28:37.620 --> 28:42.210
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

28:42.510 --> 28:46.110
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

28:46.130 --> 28:49.290
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

28:49.200 --> 28:50.720
Execute him! Execute him!

28:49.490 --> 28:51.310
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

28:51.340 --> 28:56.680
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

28:51.750 --> 28:53.030
Hurry up and execute him!

28:53.030 --> 28:54.630
It's the 3rd quarter of noon!

28:56.700 --> 28:59.180
♪ Don't live in vain ♪

28:57.400 --> 28:58.160
Execute!

29:31.990 --> 29:35.640
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

29:35.660 --> 29:38.840
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

29:36.310 --> 29:37.910
What's wrong with this girl?

29:38.860 --> 29:41.660
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

29:40.830 --> 29:41.590
Are you okay?

29:41.680 --> 29:46.100
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

29:46.460 --> 29:50.220
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

29:50.250 --> 29:53.180
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

29:53.550 --> 29:55.590
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

29:55.610 --> 30:00.640
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

30:00.680 --> 30:04.690
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

30:03.550 --> 30:04.120
Make way!

30:04.710 --> 30:07.870
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

30:05.830 --> 30:06.360
Make way!

30:06.720 --> 30:07.580
Let me through!

30:07.890 --> 30:10.710
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

30:10.730 --> 30:15.480
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

30:15.630 --> 30:19.410
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

30:19.430 --> 30:22.210
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

30:22.520 --> 30:24.360
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

30:24.390 --> 30:29.790
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

30:29.820 --> 30:35.870
♪ Don't live in vain,
have a pleasant journey of life ♪

30:47.280 --> 30:48.760
He was truly a man of steel.

30:49.200 --> 30:50.160
He endured the execution for so long

30:50.160 --> 30:51.790
without uttering a single word.

30:51.790 --> 30:53.190
How many cuts did he take?

30:53.550 --> 30:54.440
Did you count?

30:54.750 --> 30:56.200
Don't you know about

30:56.220 --> 30:57.400
Executioner Wang's skills?

30:57.400 --> 30:59.160
No one could have a good end
under his blade.

30:59.160 --> 31:00.290
There must have been

31:00.440 --> 31:01.400
at least 1,000 cuts.

31:01.400 --> 31:02.510
1,000 cuts?

31:03.440 --> 31:05.110
Could someone so strong-willed

31:05.110 --> 31:06.440
really be a corrupt official?

31:06.440 --> 31:07.840
Who can say that for sure?

31:07.880 --> 31:09.440
But the high grain prices were real,

31:09.440 --> 31:12.500
and the fact that people starved to death
was also real.

31:22.550 --> 31:23.880
Stop looking. Let's go.

31:25.840 --> 31:28.310
[Wei County]

31:27.880 --> 31:28.340
This...

31:28.400 --> 31:29.960
Snowing at this time of year?

31:29.960 --> 31:30.510
When snow falls at such a time,

31:30.510 --> 31:32.510
it means there's been a grave injustice.

31:32.510 --> 31:34.000
It shouldn't be snowing
at this time of year.

31:34.000 --> 31:34.590
What's going on?

31:34.590 --> 31:35.070
Indeed.

31:35.110 --> 31:37.350
Snowing at this time of year must mean
a great injustice has occurred.

31:37.350 --> 31:37.720
That's right.

31:37.720 --> 31:38.350
So heavy.

31:38.350 --> 31:39.810
Look how heavy the snow is.

31:43.240 --> 31:44.700
He must have been wronged.

31:46.920 --> 31:48.720
Even heaven can't bear to watch.

31:49.400 --> 31:50.200
It's snowing.

32:10.200 --> 32:11.460
Have something to eat.

32:11.510 --> 32:13.000
The authorities ordered his body
to be exposed for 3 months

32:13.000 --> 32:14.110
to appease public anger.

32:14.110 --> 32:14.720
This night

32:15.030 --> 32:16.090
is going to be long.

32:18.790 --> 32:19.450
Do you think

32:19.550 --> 32:21.410
Lord Lu was wrongfully executed?

32:22.000 --> 32:23.480
His confessions are all signed and sealed,

32:23.480 --> 32:24.510
written in black and white.

32:24.510 --> 32:26.170
There can't be any injustice.

32:26.270 --> 32:27.480
But it's snowing at this time of year.

32:27.480 --> 32:29.510
Even heaven is protesting his innocence.

32:29.510 --> 32:30.570
Do you think Lord Lu

32:30.650 --> 32:31.710
was truly wronged?

32:31.710 --> 32:32.710
Watch your words.

32:33.750 --> 32:34.510
This case was personally investigated

32:34.510 --> 32:35.550
by Lord Song,

32:35.830 --> 32:37.350
and the punishment was set
by the Court of Judicial Review.

32:37.350 --> 32:38.270
Whether it's right or wrong,

32:38.270 --> 32:39.680
the higher-ups will decide.

32:39.680 --> 32:42.340
We just need to follow orders
without question.

32:45.480 --> 32:46.210
Who's there?

32:48.400 --> 32:49.400
Where's the body?

33:08.240 --> 33:11.900
[Tomb of Lu Huai]

33:18.510 --> 33:19.510
Master said

33:20.000 --> 33:21.880
that as someone from the immortal sect,

33:21.880 --> 33:23.340
to achieve the great path,

33:23.750 --> 33:25.150
I must remain steadfast,

33:25.400 --> 33:26.510
untainted by the mortal world,

33:26.510 --> 33:28.570
and free from karmic entanglements.

33:29.350 --> 33:31.640
But this time
when I came down the mountain,

33:31.640 --> 33:32.790
I broke my vows

33:33.510 --> 33:35.720
and forcibly tied
a marriage bond with you.

33:35.720 --> 33:36.980
I regret it in my heart,

33:38.160 --> 33:40.220
but the consequences are already set

33:41.830 --> 33:43.030
and cannot be undone.

33:44.110 --> 33:45.970
All I can do now is stride forward.

33:46.960 --> 33:47.550
Lord Lu.

33:48.920 --> 33:50.250
I really must leave now.

33:50.960 --> 33:52.960
I need to get medicine for my master.

33:53.790 --> 33:54.840
But don't worry,

33:55.590 --> 33:57.440
I'll burn plenty of paper offerings
for you

33:57.440 --> 33:58.310
so you can live

33:58.510 --> 34:01.000
comfortably and peacefully
in the underworld.

34:01.000 --> 34:01.640
Also,

34:02.050 --> 34:03.110
those buried around here

34:03.110 --> 34:04.310
are all my relatives.

34:04.720 --> 34:06.320
They're all kind and gentle,

34:06.830 --> 34:08.190
and I believe they'll

34:08.400 --> 34:09.199
treat you well

34:09.510 --> 34:10.770
and get along with you.

34:43.280 --> 34:50.889
[Wei County Government]

34:43.670 --> 34:44.270
Take care.

34:44.630 --> 34:45.230
Take care.

34:51.110 --> 34:51.590
Chu.

34:52.000 --> 34:53.530
You were doing so well here.

34:53.550 --> 34:54.750
Why are you quitting?

34:54.960 --> 34:55.590
Indeed.

34:55.920 --> 34:56.850
People out there

34:56.920 --> 34:58.000
are all competing to get in

34:58.000 --> 34:59.070
and become a bailiff.

34:59.070 --> 35:00.190
It's a secure job, you know—

35:00.190 --> 35:01.280
steady for life.

35:01.440 --> 35:01.840
How...

35:01.920 --> 35:02.550
How can you just

35:02.550 --> 35:03.950
decide to quit like that?

35:03.960 --> 35:04.840
Life

35:05.190 --> 35:06.880
has different paths for everyone.

35:06.880 --> 35:08.550
I'm too restless.

35:08.880 --> 35:10.410
I'm not cut out for this job.

35:11.630 --> 35:13.430
Then what job are you cut out for?

35:15.030 --> 35:15.890
Can't you tell?

35:16.590 --> 35:17.450
With this face,

35:17.920 --> 35:19.520
I should be living off women.

35:20.230 --> 35:20.840
Alright then.

35:20.840 --> 35:21.280
I'm leaving.

35:21.280 --> 35:21.810
Alright.

35:21.920 --> 35:22.400
Take care.

35:22.400 --> 35:23.000
Take care.

35:27.280 --> 35:28.800
Chu! Chu!

35:28.960 --> 35:29.670
Chu!

35:29.670 --> 35:31.280
Don't go, Chu! Don't go!

35:31.280 --> 35:33.000
Chu, don't go!

35:33.480 --> 35:35.510
Chu, don't go!

35:36.710 --> 35:37.550
Don't go!

35:58.770 --> 36:01.050
[Tomb of Lu Huai]

36:04.760 --> 36:06.360
How long have you been awake?

36:07.360 --> 36:08.110
About 3 days.

36:10.280 --> 36:11.690
Since I was quitting the job,

36:11.690 --> 36:14.150
there has been
one drinking party after another.

36:14.150 --> 36:15.950
What can I say? I'm just popular.

36:16.880 --> 36:17.800
For a demon,

36:18.030 --> 36:21.030
you're really committed to acting human,
aren't you?

36:21.060 --> 36:21.760
Of course.

36:51.480 --> 36:53.880
What are you waiting for?
Let's keep going.

37:01.590 --> 37:03.110
Do you think the Wang family of Jinqiu

37:03.110 --> 37:04.630
is truly a family of cultivators?

37:04.630 --> 37:06.150
Is the young master of the Wang family

37:06.150 --> 37:07.270
really a cultivator?

37:07.270 --> 37:08.400
Of course it's true.

37:08.480 --> 37:09.550
I've heard their ancestors

37:09.550 --> 37:11.030
included a Nascent Soul cultivator.

37:11.030 --> 37:11.960
That's incredibly impressive.

37:11.960 --> 37:13.490
A Nascent Soul cultivator?

37:14.320 --> 37:16.650
Isn't that close to
ascending to godhood?

37:17.550 --> 37:19.190
You clearly don't understand.

37:19.190 --> 37:20.710
Cultivators in the immortal sect

37:20.710 --> 37:22.240
are divided into 10 realms:

37:22.590 --> 37:24.000
Qi Cultivation, Foundation Building,

37:24.000 --> 37:25.920
Golden Core, Nascent Soul, Cave Void,

37:25.920 --> 37:27.230
Soul Projection, Integration,

37:27.230 --> 37:28.960
Great Completion, Tribulation Crossing,

37:28.960 --> 37:30.000
and Deity Transformation.

37:30.000 --> 37:31.600
But since the God-Demon War,

37:31.960 --> 37:33.110
the heavenly ladder collapsed,

37:33.110 --> 37:35.510
and spiritual energy in the world
has become increasingly scarce,

37:35.510 --> 37:37.280
making cultivation
more difficult than ever.

37:37.280 --> 37:39.710
Not to mention Tribulation Crossing
or Deity Transformation,

37:39.710 --> 37:41.400
even Cave Void
and Soul Projection cultivators

37:41.400 --> 37:42.550
are hard to find.

37:43.590 --> 37:44.880
These days, if there's

37:45.440 --> 37:47.170
a Nascent Soul cultivator in a sect,

37:47.170 --> 37:49.170
they can dominate an entire region.

37:49.320 --> 37:51.510
The Wang family of Jinqiu
used to be so prestigious

37:51.510 --> 37:54.370
that they wouldn't even bother with
people like us.

37:55.070 --> 37:56.380
It was only after

37:56.690 --> 37:57.760
their Nascent Soul ancestor

37:57.760 --> 37:58.440
passed away

37:58.800 --> 37:59.960
that their family declined like this.

37:59.960 --> 38:01.100
I've also heard that

38:01.230 --> 38:02.280
this generation of the Wang family

38:02.280 --> 38:03.840
has no descendants
with immortal perception.

38:03.840 --> 38:05.070
Even the young master of the Wang family

38:05.070 --> 38:06.440
is also just an ordinary person.

38:06.440 --> 38:07.440
That I don't know.

38:08.110 --> 38:10.110
Anyway, all the War Demons are dead,

38:10.280 --> 38:11.920
and the Youhu Clan won't descend
from the mountains.

38:11.920 --> 38:13.420
The Twelve Immortal Sects
have all the power now.

38:13.420 --> 38:14.760
Even the Emperor himself

38:14.760 --> 38:16.160
has to show them respect.

38:17.760 --> 38:18.280
Gentlemen,

38:18.280 --> 38:19.280
here's your wine.

38:19.440 --> 38:20.240
Please enjoy.

38:23.840 --> 38:24.370
Want one?

38:24.720 --> 38:25.320
Nah.

38:26.000 --> 38:27.330
Just drinking, no food?

38:27.880 --> 38:28.360
Yep,

38:28.840 --> 38:30.480
just drinking, no food.

38:30.840 --> 38:32.000
You know me.

38:34.280 --> 38:36.280
So you still don't feel like eating.

38:44.960 --> 38:45.480
Hu.

38:45.840 --> 38:46.640
Take a break.

38:46.800 --> 38:47.590
Come and have some water.

38:47.590 --> 38:48.030
Okay.

38:49.280 --> 38:50.670
The road is rough. Be careful.

38:50.670 --> 38:52.960
This uneven road needs to be leveled.

38:54.040 --> 38:55.440
Otherwise, someone might fall
and break their teeth,

38:55.440 --> 38:57.030
and no one's going to take care of them.

38:57.030 --> 38:58.760
I have my wife to take care of me.

39:09.110 --> 39:09.800
Xin Mei.

39:11.000 --> 39:11.550
Thank you

39:12.150 --> 39:13.550
for agreeing to marry me.

39:14.710 --> 39:15.320
Lord Lu.

39:16.280 --> 39:17.880
Do you have any other wishes?

39:19.670 --> 39:20.400
As your wife,

39:21.030 --> 39:22.890
is there anything I can do for you?

39:25.960 --> 39:26.920
I still feel that

39:27.030 --> 39:28.110
Lord Lu's punishment

39:28.110 --> 39:29.710
was determined too hastily.

39:29.800 --> 39:30.840
In the past, the Court of Judicial Review

39:30.840 --> 39:32.400
had sentenced officials to
death by 1,000 cuts before,

39:32.400 --> 39:33.880
but such an inhumane and cruel punishment

39:33.880 --> 39:35.630
normally had to be reported step by step—

39:35.630 --> 39:37.230
from the prefecture and county
up to the capital,

39:37.230 --> 39:38.760
until the Emperor approved it.

39:38.760 --> 39:39.160
Yet...

39:39.440 --> 39:40.460
Yet Lord Lu's crime

39:40.460 --> 39:42.520
was decided in less than half a month.

39:42.550 --> 39:42.960
No.

39:43.190 --> 39:45.050
This matter cannot end like this.

39:48.190 --> 39:48.710
Miss.

39:49.510 --> 39:50.710
This road is difficult,

39:50.710 --> 39:51.840
and there are landslides.

39:51.840 --> 39:53.500
This road is full of potholes.

39:53.560 --> 39:54.550
You're all alone.

39:54.550 --> 39:56.590
If you fall,
there won't be anyone to help you up.

39:56.590 --> 39:58.320
You should find an easier path.

39:58.920 --> 40:00.650
Come on, let's get back to work.

40:09.480 --> 40:10.550
Excuse me, gentlemen.

40:10.550 --> 40:11.880
Could you please tell me

40:12.000 --> 40:12.880
how to get to the capital?
